{"tid":1059671,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"利捲入醜聞案件缺席頒獎禮 容祖兒：我同佢都唔熟","createTime":"2019-03-13T09:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T11:22:35.000Z","uid":122167,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cee590ce39f43ff95fa294e2769d88b9e957e87e","tid":1059671,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boFGnh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FboFGnh8.jpg&h=4f1eb1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRxUHic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRxUHic.jpg&h=de61d438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n奪得「年度風雲歌手」的容祖兒，由6名韓國舞蹈員伴舞下壓軸登場，唱出新歌《Pretty Crazy》。騷後接受《香港01》訪問時說：「勝利嚟唔到對我同觀眾嚟講係好可惜又遺憾嘅事，本身由合唱變成咗獨唱，因本上個月佢好忙，後期有好多工作都要佢幫手但都要叫停，所以對我嚟講好可惜。」<br />\n<br />\n（被問到合作時有冇察覺勝利有異樣？）Joey坦言說：「咁又冇，佢又好專注喺我哋兩個合作時工作上面，我都被蒙在鼓裏，乜都唔知道。」（覺得佢為人點？）「覺得佢為人好聰明，好機靈啦，又好有才華，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>其實我又同佢又唔係好熟</ins></span></strong>，不過我對佢嘅評價都好正面嘅，希望佢哋嘅歌迷唔好咁唔開心，都知道偶像有事啲歌迷會好大打擊，我作為歌迷都會繼續支持Bigbang。」"},{"pid":"4b26c014ea8d74c6f827593f68ce64f6a9ffe3bc","tid":1059671,"uid":19624,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"我都被蒙在鼓裏<br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到人地呃埋你"},{"pid":"89ec68b5d31ece81d54871257d56d31a41c0ec40","tid":1059671,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b26c014ea8d74c6f827593f68ce64f6a9ffe3bc","tid":1059671,"uid":19624,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"我都被蒙在鼓裏<br />\n<br />\n屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到人地呃埋你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c50f